### Health Check - Verify backend is running
GET http://localhost:3001/ping

### Get All Todo Lists - Should return seeded data
GET http://localhost:3001/api/lists

### Get All Todo Lists with Accept Header
GET http://localhost:3001/api/lists
Accept: application/json

### Test 404 Route - Should return not found error
GET http://localhost:3001/api/nonexistent

### Health Check with verbose headers
GET http://localhost:3001/ping
User-Agent: VSCode REST Client
Accept: application/json

### Test CORS headers
GET http://localhost:3001/api/lists
Origin: http://localhost:3000

